data.description: Completely Updated Highland Park 4 Bed 2 Bath Home! Nearly 2,000 sq ft with huge Family area bonus room addition. Hardwood floors, Brand new luxury vinyl flooring, new carpet and paint. Fully Renovated Open concept eat in kitchen. Massive bonus space with vaulted ceilings, makes a great family room. Basement features a 3rd living room with 2 additional bedrooms and bathroom. The basement also has a kitchenette with sink and stove. Huge corner lot with an oversized 2 car garage. RV/ Boat parking in the rear. This home is better then new and turnkey. Close to everything!
